word_mean_info__list.difference: 用于人时，指地位优于其他人；用于物时，指该物在大小、重要性等方面优于他物。
侧重指具有影响力或凝聚力。从而有主导和引导的作用。
通常不用于人。用于物时，指在重要性方面占第一位。
侧重指在行进或发展过程中居首位。
着重指因重要性、意义、优越或重大而名列同类之首。
指同其他人或其它物、问题等相比较，显得更加重要和突出。
拽人时，表同类中职位最高，权力最大；指物时，表同类中最重要，价值最高。
通常只用于物。指在一定范围内，某物的重要性、体积或力量等超过其它物。
可与作“初步的，初级”的elementary换用。
强调属于事物的基础或本质。
指属于事物的初步或起始阶段

bilingual.target: 这个问题是二次的，不是主要的。

bilingual.source: The lungs are the primary organ for respiration.
Social media has become a primary channel of communication.
bilingual.target: 社交媒体已经成为主要的传播渠道。

bilingual.source: Family is the primary agent of socialization for most individuals.
bilingual.target: 对大多数人来说，家庭是主要的社会化代理。

bilingual.source: The carriage was a primary mode of transport in ancient times.
bilingual.target: 四轮马车在古代是主要的交通工具。

bilingual.source: The ox cart was a primary means of transportation in the past.
bilingual.target: 牛车在过去是主要的运输工具。

bilingual.source: Many vegetarians rely on legume as a primary source of protein.
bilingual.target: 许多素食者依靠豆类植物作为主要的蛋白质来源。

bilingual.source: Many countries use value-added tax as a primary source of revenue.
bilingual.target: 许多国家都采用增值税作为主要的税收来源。

bilingual.source: Many schools use phonics as a primary method for teaching reading.
bilingual.target: 许多学校使用自然拼读法作为主要的阅读教学方法。

bilingual.source: In a matrifocal family, the mother is the primary authority figure.
bilingual.target: 在一个以母亲为中心的家庭中，母亲是主要的权威人物。

list.abstract: primary，英语单词，有初期的，原始的，初等的，原始的，基本的等意思。

yingyinNormal.en: What's in the spray specifically? The primary ingredient is Bacitracin.
yingyinNormal.zh: 等等，这个喷雾的主要成分是什么？喷雾的主要成分是"杆菌肽"。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, that is one of my degrees. My primary field is neuroscience.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是我的学位之一，我的主修是神经系统学。

yingyinNormal.en: It's talc. But as that's a primary ingredient of baby powder, I understand your confusion.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是滑石粉，但由于滑石粉是婴儿爽身粉的原材料，你会搞错也是人之常情。

yingyinNormal.en: Where am I? This is the Alcazar of Kalique Abrasax, second primary of the house of Abrasax.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是哪？这里是凯莉克阿拜萨斯的城堡，是阿拜萨斯的第二大城堡。

yingyinNormal.en: And I have to say, everyone's primary focus right now needs to be on the Miller family, not this.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而且我得说，大家现在应该首要关注米勒一家，而非此事。

yingyinNormal.en: I work for an organization whose primary purpose is not space travel. It's reshaping wrongdoings.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我所工作的组织，其主首要目标不是探索太空而是修正历史错误。

yingyinNormal.en: No, I'm not here for the primary. I'm here to run for the 30th, and I want you to run my campaign.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，我不是为初选而来的，我想竞选30选区议员，我希望你做我的竞选经理。

yingyinNormal.en: When Claire first came down here to Dallas, we said it was to lay the groundwork for the Texas primary.
yingyinNormal.zh: 克莱尔最初来到达拉斯时，我们说是为德州的初选打基础。

yingyinNormal.en: My primary concern with being granted tenure is living with an insanely jealous roommate after the fact.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我最大担心的是，在拿到终身教职后，还得跟超嫉妒我的室友同住一个屋檐下。

yingyinNormal.en: Huge IQ, great performance in primary school. And it all went tits up. Drugs, petty crime, never had a job.
yingyinNormal.zh: 高智商，小学时表现极为出色，然后一落千丈。吸毒，小偷小摸，游手好闲。

yingyinNormal.en: Then, when we started, the hosts' emotions were primary colors. Love, hate. I wanted all the shades in between.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们研究之初，接待员的情感都如原色单调，喜爱，厌恶，我希望在其中加入所有的颜色。

yingyinNormal.en: With our primary fleet engaged in the Laurentian system, I hereby order all cadets to report to hangar 1 immediately. Dismissed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 除在劳伦星系执勤的舰队，现在我要求所有学员马上前往第一库区。解散。

yingyinNormal.en: There are three primary theories concerning sediment flow rate. Each of these theories can be further sub-categorized into two distinct...
yingyinNormal.zh: 沉积速率有三个主要理论，每一个还可以细分为两个…

yingyinNormal.en: Oh. Okay. Okay. There are three primary theories concerning sediment flow rate. Each of these theories can be further sub-categorized into…
yingyinNormal.zh: 好，沉积速率有三个主要理论，每一个还可以细分为两个…

yingyinNormal.en: When Underwood loses, you'll spend the next two years fighting off a primary opponent. Every one of our 200,000 members in Ohio will turn on you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 等安德伍德输了，你接下来两年可就有仗要打了，我们在俄亥俄的二十万会员都会反对你。

yingyinNormal.en: Point of inquiry, given that Leonard is your secondary friend and Koothrappali is your primary friend, why didn't you seek refuge under his roof?
yingyinNormal.zh: 有个问题，既然莱纳德是你的第二好友，库萨帕里才是你的头号好友，你为什么没去他那？

yingyinNormal.en: I'm commending Governor Sally Morrison of the great state of Arizona, for giving us all such a good example of voting centers as used in their recent primary.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我赞扬伟大的亚利桑那州的州长萨莉·莫里森，因为她在最近的初选中为我们树立了，投票中心的好榜样。

yingyinNormal.en: Man, I feel sorry for them. Gotta run home to their owners! Not us. Now is back to our primary mission. The down fall of the human race. It is on, humans! It is on!
yingyinNormal.zh: 真为他们感到悲哀，得回家找主人。我们不用。现在要继续进行我们最重要的任务，毁灭人类。开战了，人类！开战了！

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Requiring companies to make gender the <highlight>primary</highlight> qualification for board membership will inevitably lead to less experienced private sector boards.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 要求企业将性别作为成为董事会成员的主要资格，将不可避免地导致私营部门董事会经验不足。

examination_example.sentence: The growth of the use of English as the world's <highlight>primary</highlight> language for international communication has obviously been continuing for several decades.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 几十年来，英语作为世界主要国际交流语言的使用明显持续增长。

examination_example.sentence: The quality of writings is of <highlight>primary</highlight> importance.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 作品的质量是最重要的。

sense_info_list.en: relating to education for children between the ages of about five and ten

examination_example.sentence: Suppose you are working for the "Aiding Rural <highlight>Primary</highlight> School" project of your university.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 假设你正在为你所在大学的“援助农村小学”项目工作。

examination_example.sentence: The opposition claims <highlight>primary</highlight> school pupils doing at least two hours of sport a week have nearly halved.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 反对派声称，每周至少运动两个小时的小学生几乎减少了一半。

examination_example.sentence: Alongside that, many countries are introducing English into the <highlight>primary</highlight>-school curriculum.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 与此同时，许多国家正在将英语引入小学课程。

指“初步的、基础的”，着重指基本的或开始的事物。
主要指形成事物核心部分“不可缺少的”，也可指“内在或本质上的”。
指“基础的根本的、首要的”，主要修饰无形的、抽象的事物。

数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence_trans: 政府将采取行动解决中小学生沉重的课外负担问题。

examination_example.sentence: Jane talked with a <highlight>primary</highlight> school student about Chinese culture.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 简和一名小学生谈论中国文化。

examination_example.sentence: Activities will also be held during the festival, such as showing the <highlight>primary</highlight> posters and writings, and opera costumes.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 节日期间还将举行活动，如展示重要的海报和作品，以及戏曲服装。

word_usage.usage: primary不用于比较等级，在句中只用作定语。

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: 通常不用于人。用于物时，指在重要性方面占第一位。
通常只用于物。指在一定范围内，某物的重要性、体积或力量等超过其它物。
侧重指具有影响力或凝聚力，从而有主导和引导的作用。
着重指因重要性、意义、优越或重大程度而名列同类之首。
